OL,3,CGPs across England vote overwhelmingly
OL,4,Cto take collective action
OL,6,FGP practices will be able to choose to
OL,7,Fimplement as few or as many of these
OL,8,Factions as they want, with doctors
OL,9,Fsaying the action could last for
OL,10,F"months".
OL,12,FThe BMA described the development as
OL,13,F"an act of desperation", while the
OL,14,FRoyal College of GPs said it shows the
OL,15,F"strength of feeling" among family
OL,16,Fdoctors in England.
OL,18,FNHS England has urged patients to come
OL,19,Fforward for care as normal during the
OL,20,Fperiod of collective action.
