OL,3,CGPs across England vote overwhelmingly
OL,4,Cto take collective action
OL,6,FPractices will still be required to
OL,7,Fopen between 8am to 6.30pm Monday to
OL,8,FFriday.
OL,10,FThe BMA has said the new GP contract,
OL,11,Fwhich will see services given a 1.9%
OL,12,Ffunding increase for 2024/25, means
OL,13,Fmany surgeries will struggle to stay
OL,14,Ffinancially viable.
